episodes.title: Hillary Clinton does not appear for scheduled deposition at Jeffrey Epstein hearing
episodes.description:
House Oversight Committee Chair James Comer talks to reporters after Hillary Clinton did not appear for a scheduled deposition with the panel.

Former President Bill Clinton and former Secretary of State Hillary Clinton may face legal action after they failed to appear at a House Oversight Committee hearing Tuesday morning. The committee was planning to question them about their reported connection with late convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein. 

Via: CNN
